  "prompt": "Where can I find the glasses that Emma Watson wears?",
  "response": "Emma Watson is known for her elegant and sophisticated eyewear choices, often reflecting her commitment to sustainable fashion. While she has been seen wearing a variety of styles from different designers, here are some options and tips to help you find similar glasses:\n\n### **1. Sustainable and Ethical Brands**\nEmma often opts for brands that align with her values of sustainability and ethical production. Consider exploring the following brands:\n\n- **Warby Parker**: Offers stylish frames with a home try-on program. They also have a socially responsible model, donating a pair for every pair sold.\n  - [Warby Parker Website](https://www.warbyparker.com/)\n  \n- **Proof Eyewear**: Known for their eco-friendly materials and handcrafted designs.\n  - [Proof Eyewear Website](https://www.iwantproofframes.com/)\n  \n- **Etnia Barcelona**: Features vibrant and unique patterns with a focus on sustainable practices.\n  - [Etnia Barcelona Website](https://www.etniabarcelona.com/)\n\n### **2. Designer Brands**\nEmma has been spotted wearing high-end designer frames that exude timeless style:\n\n- **Dior**: Offers luxurious and chic eyewear perfect for a sophisticated look.\n  - [Dior Eyewear](https://www.dior.com/en_us/fragrance-eyewear)\n\n- **Oliver Peoples**: Known for their classic and understated designs.\n  - [Oliver Peoples Website](https://www.oliverpeoples.com/)\n\n- **Persol**: Features iconic and stylish frames that blend modernity with tradition.\n  - [Persol Eyewear](https://www.persol.com/)\n\n### **3. Classic and Versatile Styles**\nIf you're looking for something versatile that resembles Emma's style, consider:\n\n- **Round Frames**: Emma has been seen wearing elegant round sunglasses and optical frames.\n  - Available at stores like [Ray-Ban](https://www.ray-ban.com/) or [Sunglass Hut](https://www.sunglasshut.com/).\n\n- **Cat-Eye Frames**: For a touch of vintage charm, cat-eye glasses are a great option.\n  - Available at [Moscot](https://moscot.com/) or [Nordstrom](https://www.nordstrom.com/).\n\n### **4. Custom and Boutique Options**\nFor a unique pair tailored to your preferences:\n\n- **Local Opticians**: Many local optical stores offer custom frame options.\n- **Boutique Brands**: Explore boutique eyewear brands that offer unique and limited-edition designs.\n\n### **5. Checking Recent Appearances**\nFashion choices can vary over time, so to find the most current eyewear Emma Watson is wearing:\n\n- **Social Media**: Follow Emma Watson\u2019s official Instagram or other social media profiles where she might share her latest looks.\n  \n- **Fashion Magazines and Websites**: Publications like Vogue, Harper\u2019s Bazaar, and Elle often feature her style choices and may mention specific brands or designers.\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Glasses:**\n\n1. **Face Shape**: Select frames that complement your face shape. For example, round frames suit square faces, while cat-eye frames enhance oval faces.\n2. **Material**: Choose materials that are comfortable and durable, such as acetate, metal, or sustainable options like bamboo.\n3. **Lens Type**: Consider whether you need prescription lenses, UV protection, or specific tints for your lifestyle.\n4. **Fit and Comfort**: Ensure the glasses fit well and feel comfortable for extended wear.\n\nBy exploring these options and keeping Emma Watson's style in mind, you can find a pair of glasses that not only match her elegant aesthetic but also suit your personal style and values.",
